        {"name": "highlyRatedConditionsCount", "type": "Nullable(Int32)", "comment": "The count of medical conditions for which the provider has received high ratings, reflecting their areas of expertise.. Samples: ['{\'highlyRatedConditionsCount\': 3}', '{\'highlyRatedConditionsCount\': 4}', '{\'highlyRatedConditionsCount\': 11}']"},
