        {"name": "orgWebsite", "type": "Nullable(String)", "comment": "The website URL of the provider\'s affiliated organization, where additional information and resources may be available.. Samples: ['{\'orgWebsite\': \'https://www.stmaryshealthcaresystem.org/medical-group/\'}', '{\'orgWebsite\': \'www.paeyes.com/\'}', '{\'orgWebsite\': \'www.emoryhealthcare.org/\'}']"},
